Necros are much better soloers (outdoors).  Our pets are better (stronger, more HP, etc.), but necros have fear, mez, root, lich, DoTs, FD - and the list goes on.  They were designed, it appears, to solo.  Mage can kill MUCH faster, but soloing is harder, with more downtime.  We solo by dishing out as much damage as quickly as we can.  Necros solo by killing steadily, with almost no fear of death.  Necros actually can dish out a lot more damage over time, but we dish out a lot more damage quickly.<br>
<br>
So overall - no question, necros win for soloing hands down.<br>
<br>
Bards are pretty good at soloing after level 35 or so, they get DoTs, DD, snare, stun, super sow, fear, charm, mez, etc.  So they have all the tools, but they are so wanted in groups they don't need to solo that much. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umathas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mathas</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://mathas.tripod.com/leafico.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 134<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/01 8:18:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=290.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://mathas.tripod.com/faceico.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: MAGE vs. NECRO---Whos the best Solo Artist?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Necros are much better soloers (outdoors)<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
